task.summary: Setup for a Spring project, including a controller. WIP: Starting to move the application to "Application". Started adding tests.

Added AdventOfCodeController to ask for the solutions of a specific day with e.g. http://localhost:8080/day?day=1&part=1 Does not handle exceptions very well (and no HTTP error codes) and not happy with the casting of the class yet.
